<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>To deposit or secure in a warehouse.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To place in the warehouse of the government or
customhouse stores, to be kept until duties are paid.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Warehouseman</ent>⟦br⟧
